<p>
<h1>Get count of API Resources for Company App</h1> 
</p>

<div class="row">
	<div class="span6" style="width:340px;"><p>
		<b>API Platform Base Path:</b>
		<p>https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{org_name}</p>
		<b>API Resource Path:</b>
		<p>/companies/{companyName}/apps/{appname}?query=count&amp;entity=apiresources</p>
		<p>
		Gets the count API Resources for a Company App
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="span6" style="width:340px;">
		<p>
		<b>Verb:</b>
		<span class="verb-GET">GET</span>
		</p>
		<b>Auth:</b>
		Basic Auth
		</p>


	</div>
</div>

<div class="span18">
	<p>
	Gets a count of APi resources (URIs) consumed by a Company App. The API resources (URIs) are aggregated across all API products with which the Company App is associated.
	</p>

	<b>cURL:</b>
	<pre>curl -u myname:mypass https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{myorg}/companies/{companyName}/apps/{appName}?query=count&amp;entity=apiresources</pre>



<b>Sample Response:</b> 
	<pre>{
  "value" : 3
}</pre>




</div>


            </div>
        </div><!--/row-->
